WITH group_data AS (
  SELECT 
    (item->>'JID')::VARCHAR AS jid,
    (item->>'Name')::VARCHAR AS name
  FROM jsonb_array_elements($1::jsonb) AS item
)
INSERT INTO groups (chat_id, name, status, created_at, updated_at)
SELECT 
  REPLACE(jid, '@g.us', '') AS chat_id,
  name,
  'inactive',
  NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo',
  NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
FROM group_data
WHERE jid IS NOT NULL AND name IS NOT NULL
ON CONFLICT (chat_id) 
DO UPDATE SET 
  name = EXCLUDED.name,
  updated_at = NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
RETURNING 
  chat_id,
  name,
  CASE 
    WHEN xmax = 0 THEN 'inserted'
    ELSE 'updated' 
  END as action_taken;

-- Query para atualizar nome do grupo pelo chat_id
-- Input: chat_id (string) e group_name (string) do n칩 anterior

UPDATE groups 
SET 
    name = $2::TEXT,
    updated_at = NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
WHERE chat_id = $1::TEXT
RETURNING 
    json_build_object(
        'status', 'success',
        'updated_group', json_build_object(
            'id', id,
            'chat_id', chat_id,
            'nome_anterior', 'N/A',
            'nome_atual', name,
            'status', status,
            'atualizado_em', updated_at
        ),
        'mensagem', 'Nome do grupo atualizado com sucesso'
    ) as resultado;

-- Query para inserir/atualizar membros de um grupo espec칤fico
WITH 
-- Buscar o grupo pelo chat_id
target_group AS (
  SELECT id as group_id, name as group_name, chat_id
  FROM groups 
  WHERE chat_id = $1::TEXT
  LIMIT 1
),

-- Preparar dados dos participantes atuais (extrair do JSONB)
current_participants AS (
  SELECT 
    jsonb_array_elements_text($2::JSONB) as phone
),

-- Inserir/atualizar membros na tabela members
upserted_members AS (
  INSERT INTO members (phone, name, status, created_at, updated_at)
  SELECT 
    cp.phone,
    'Usu치rio', -- Nome padr칚o j치 que n칚o temos o nome real
    'active',
    NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo',
    NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
  FROM current_participants cp
  ON CONFLICT (phone) 
  DO UPDATE SET 
    status = 'active',
    updated_at = NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
  RETURNING id, phone, name, status
),

-- Inserir/atualizar relacionamentos na tabela members_groups
upserted_member_groups AS (
  INSERT INTO members_groups (member_id, group_id, status, joined_at, updated_at)
  SELECT 
    um.id,
    tg.group_id,
    'active',
    NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo',
    NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
  FROM upserted_members um
  JOIN current_participants cp ON cp.phone = um.phone
  CROSS JOIN target_group tg
  ON CONFLICT (member_id, group_id)
  DO UPDATE SET 
    status = 'active',
    left_at = NULL,
    updated_at = NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
  RETURNING member_id, group_id, status, updated_at
),

-- Marcar como inativos os membros que n칚o est칚o mais no grupo
deactivated_members AS (
  UPDATE members_groups 
  SET 
    status = 'inactive',
    left_at = NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo',
    updated_at = NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo'
  WHERE group_id = (SELECT group_id FROM target_group)
  AND status = 'active'
  AND member_id IN (
    SELECT m.id 
    FROM members m 
    WHERE m.phone NOT IN (
      SELECT jsonb_array_elements_text($2::JSONB)
    )
  )
  RETURNING member_id, group_id, status
),

-- Contadores para o resultado
stats AS (
  SELECT 
    tg.group_id,
    tg.group_name,
    tg.chat_id,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM upserted_members) as members_processed,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM upserted_member_groups) as member_groups_processed,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM deactivated_members) as members_deactivated,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM current_participants) as total_current_participants
  FROM target_group tg
)

-- Resultado final
SELECT json_build_object(
  'status', CASE WHEN EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM target_group) THEN 'success' ELSE 'group_not_found' END,
  'group_info', (
    SELECT json_build_object(
      'group_id', group_id,
      'group_name', group_name,
      'chat_id', chat_id
    )
    FROM stats
  ),
  'processing_summary', (
    SELECT json_build_object(
      'total_current_participants', total_current_participants,
      'members_processed', members_processed,
      'member_groups_processed', member_groups_processed,
      'members_deactivated', members_deactivated
    )
    FROM stats
  ),
  'timestamp', NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'America/Sao_Paulo',
  'message', CASE 
    WHEN EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM target_group) THEN 'Membros do grupo sincronizados com sucesso'
    ELSE 'Grupo n칚o encontrado na base de dados'
  END
) as resultado;
